&lt;h4 id="intervals">&lt;strong>Intervals&lt;/strong>
&lt;a href="#intervals">
&lt;svg class="anchor-symbol" aria-hidden="true" height="26" width="26" viewBox="0 0 22 22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
&lt;path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="currentColor">&lt;/path>
&lt;path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76.0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71.0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71.0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76.0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z">&lt;/path>
&lt;/svg>
&lt;/a>
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>The confidence intervals are visualized using the gray ribbon. The default interval is 0.9, but can be changed using the &lt;code>conf_level&lt;/code> argument.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">
&lt;pre class='chroma'>&lt;code class='language-r' data-lang='r'>&lt;span>&lt;span class='nv'>segment_logistic&lt;/span> &lt;span class='o'>&lt;a href='https://magrittr.tidyverse.org/reference/pipe.html'>%&amp;gt;%&lt;/a>&lt;/span> &lt;/span>
&lt;span> &lt;span class='nf'>&lt;a href='https://probably.tidymodels.org/reference/cal_plot_breaks.html'>cal_plot_breaks&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;span class='o'>(&lt;/span>&lt;span class='nv'>Class&lt;/span>, &lt;span class='nv'>.pred_good&lt;/span>, conf_level &lt;span class='o'>=&lt;/span> &lt;span class='m'>0.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class='o'>)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="figs/unnamed-chunk-12-1.png" alt="Calibration plot with a confidence interval set to 0.8" width="700px" style="display: block; margin: auto;" />&lt;/p>
&lt;/div>
&lt;p>If desired, the intervals can be removed by setting the &lt;code>include_ribbon&lt;/code> argument to &lt;code>FALSE&lt;/code>.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">
&lt;pre class='chroma'>&lt;code class='language-r' data-lang='r'>&lt;span>&lt;span class='nv'>segment_logistic&lt;/span> &lt;span class='o'>&lt;a href='https://magrittr.tidyverse.org/reference/pipe.html'>%&amp;gt;%&lt;/a>&lt;/span> &lt;/span>
&lt;span> &lt;span class='nf'>&lt;a href='https://probably.tidymodels.org/reference/cal_plot_breaks.html'>cal_plot_breaks&lt;/a>&lt;/span>&lt;span class='o'>(&lt;/span>&lt;span class='nv'>Class&lt;/span>, &lt;span class='nv'>.pred_good&lt;/span>, include_ribbon &lt;span class='o'>=&lt;/span> &lt;span class='kc'>FALSE&lt;/span>&lt;span class='o'>)&lt;/span>&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="figs/unnamed-chunk-13-1.png" alt="Calibration plot with the confidence interval ribbon turned off" width="700px" style="display: block; margin: auto;" />&lt;/p>
